637
01:15:48.970 --> 01:15:58.970
gospođo.

638
01:16:38.370 --> 01:16:40.756
1:04 ujutro.

639
01:16:40.780 --> 01:16:49.026
Dođe žena kući i ništa do sedam
ujutro kad dođu spremačice.


640
01:16:49.050 --> 01:16:53.586
Stop.  Premotaj malo unazad.

641
01:16:53.610 --> 01:16:57.166
Premotati.

642
